heading: Applying to G.A.D. Elementary School
paragraph1: Thank you for your interest in G.A.D. Elementary School. We understand that selecting a school for their child is a significant decision for parents. We offer an excellent educational experience in a very conducive environment, where students excel in their academic, athletic and artistic pursuits. Children seeking admission from Grade 1 to 9 will have to take a written Math and English placement test.
paragraph2: Note: We also run a Preschool in the campus and accept children who are three years old. The admission to Preschool is ongoing. For more information please contact the main school office (604-595-0888) or visit to see the Preschool in action. We invite all applying families to visit our school while school is in session. We offer tours of the school to families on working days. Interested families may please contact the front desk to schedule a family visit. The following information must be submitted with the application: At GAD, We make our admissions process as simple and as straight forward as possible.
step2Text: Make payment of $350 ( non-refundable & non-transferable Registration Fee) payable to G.A.D. Elementary School (re-enrollment registration fee is $200)
step3Text: Attach the following documents with application Form

step3Points.point: A Copy of Child’s Birth Certificate
Citizenship Cards/PR Cards/Immigrant Visa of the parent
